# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# MiniDora v2 — Environment Configuration
# Copy this file to server/.env and fill in real values.
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# TIER 1: vLLM — Primary AI inference server
# Run locally: https://docs.vllm.ai/en/latest/getting_started/quickstart.html
# docker run -p 8000:8000 vllm/vllm-openai --model mistralai/Mistral-7B-Instruct-v0.2
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
VLLM_URL=http://localhost:8000
VLLM_MODEL=mistralai/Mistral-7B-Instruct-v0.2

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# TIER 2: Ollama — Local AI fallback (auto-activates if vLLM fails)
# Install: https://ollama.com/download
# Then run: ollama pull llama3.2
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
OLLAMA_FALLBACK_URL=http://localhost:11434
OLLAMA_MODEL=llama3.2

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# TIER 3: OpenRouter — External AI fallback (budget-controlled)
# Get free key: https://openrouter.ai
# Many free models available (llama, mistral, etc.)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
OPENROUTER_API_KEY=sk-or-your-key-here
OPENROUTER_MODEL=meta-llama/llama-3.1-8b-instruct:free
MONTHLY_BUDGET_LIMIT=10

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# LEGACY: Gemini keys (still supported as Tier 3 fallback)
# If OPENROUTER_API_KEY is not set, Gemini keys are used instead.
# Get free keys: https://aistudio.google.com/apikey
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# GEMINI_API_KEYS=key1,key2,key3
# GEMINI_API_KEY=single-key-here
# GEMINI_MODEL=gemini-2.0-flash

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# REDIS — Semantic cache + memory layer
# Free cloud: https://upstash.com (copy the redis:// URL)
# Local:      redis://localhost:6379
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
REDIS_URL=redis://localhost:6379

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# OBSERVABILITY — Langfuse (optional, silent if not set)
# Free plan: https://cloud.langfuse.com
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# LANGFUSE_PUBLIC_KEY=pk-lf-your-public-key
# LANGFUSE_SECRET_KEY=sk-lf-your-secret-key
# LANGFUSE_HOST=https://cloud.langfuse.com

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# MONGODB — Persistent chat history (optional)
# Free cluster: https://cloud.mongodb.com
# Without this, chats use localStorage only.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# MONGODB_URI=mongodb+srv://user:pass@cluster.mongodb.net/?retryWrites=true
# MONGODB_DB=minidora

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# SERVER
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
PORT=3001
NODE_ENV=development

# Production: restrict CORS to your frontend domain
# CLIENT_ORIGIN=https://your-app.vercel.app
